{"tid":1253321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方] 私家車駛入激流致5人被困　原因竟是為洗車","createTime":"2019-06-23T13:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:51:00.000Z","uid":147916,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cf94d55deac2f1e4bc98f08d8fab5219b86c91","tid":1253321,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Etk9OAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtk9OAf.jpg&h=50d2649c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也許因為「洗車費」太貴，車主難以負擔，內地不時有車主把私家車駛入湖水或河水中清洗。浙江麗水市一名鍾姓男子日前駕車接載家人，前往太平鄉享受田園樂時，鍾男發現私家車太髒，竟駕車駛進太平溪清洗，卻因水流湍急結果被困，最終要消防趕到現場營救。<br />\n<br />\n當地消防接獲市民求助後，派出2輛消防車、12名消防員到場營救。消防趕到後，發現河流闊約50多米，私家車距岸邊近20米，雖然河水不深，但有明顯坡度，河水流速非常快，而車內有2男2女及1名年約3歲小孩。消防其後決定，冒險涉水用牽引繩固定私家車後，讓被困5人穿上救生衣，再拉着繩索緩緩走上岸。<br />\n<br />\n40多分鐘後，消防終把所有被困者救出。上岸後仍驚魂未定的鍾男，透露當天他與妻女，以及弟弟及其女友前往太平鄉摘西瓜，途中發現車身太髒，便把私家車駛進河中。未料不到幾秒，「車子就被水流沖了個90度大轉彎」，鍾男雖嘗試離開，惟引擎出現故障。無計可施下，他只好報警求助。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190623/bkn-20190623051136022-0623_00952_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3iAIhspSKnStKc30ahpsHRhI5Iwa_SjwgZY9gJVLVbd9OWCXwf_LpcvZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190623%2Fbkn-20190623051136022-0623_00952_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3iAIhspSKnStKc30ahpsHRhI5Iwa_SjwgZY9gJVLVbd9OWCXwf_LpcvZM&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1wRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=23eecdf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190623/bkn-20190623051136022-0623_00952_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3iAIhspSKnStKc30ahpsHRhI5Iwa_SjwgZY9gJVLVbd9OWCXwf_LpcvZM</a>"},{"pid":"eb21428ff34ddd02b9794466ed7bd0d3f213ce7b","tid":1253321,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"反轉黎洗呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478e839aea2d2329f56fb407f604b0cf23fe2187","tid":1253321,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb21428ff34ddd02b9794466ed7bd0d3f213ce7b","tid":1253321,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"反轉黎洗呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"反轉洗乾淨啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e36662e24c06b01005368fe67509ac65326faee","tid":1253321,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"大陸成日有類似新聞"}]}